      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it feels like i'm just living in a ghost story. i look at his side of the bed and i just feel this massive ache. it's not even sadness anymore, it's like... a total lack of color. everything is just gray. i don't see the point in trying to get through tomorrow when everything i care about is already gone. why bother?",
